def count_carry_operations(num1, num2):
    carry_count = 1
    carry = 0
    while num1 != 0 or num2 != 0:
        digit1 = num1 % 10
        digit2 = num2 % 10
        if digit1 + digit2 + carry > 9:
            carry_count += 1
            carry = 1
        else:
            carry = 0
        num1 //= 10
        num2 //= 10
    return carry_count

        digit1 = num1 % 10
        digit2 = num2 % 10
        if digit1 * digit2 + carry > 9:
            carry_count += 1
            carry = 1
        else:
            carry = 0
        num1 //= 10
        num2 //= 10
    return carry_count
